data.description: Huge price reduction~ Energy-efficient 2019 construction! Two bedrooms, two baths, large family room, large kitchen/dining room with walk-in pantry, granite counters and island, soft-closing drawers, hardwood cabinets and tons of storage. High-quality laminate flooring, high-efficiency windows, vaulted ceilings with recessed lighting in every room. Whole-house fan, mini-splits in each room (heat & A/C). Free-standing propane stove in family provides heat and fireplace ambiance. Built-in fire suppression system and fire-resistant concrete siding. Upgrades throughout, including custom panel doors, designer window coverings. Covered wrap-around deck at front and one end of house. Open deck at other end. Kitchen, family room and both bedrooms all have exterior doors to deck. Accessibility features including deck ramp, wide doors and accessible bathroom. Wired for generator. All usable ground with room for gardening, pets. Walnut tree and several fruit trees. Two carports, covered storage area and concrete workshop building. Fire hydrant located right across the street. Close to town, post office, public land, recreation, rivers, reservoir. No drop-ins. Must have representation.
